<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../824/140824.xml">
Ronald Fisher</link></scientist>
</person>
, is a <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../912/430912.xml">
kernel</link>. It was introduced in 1998 by Tommi Jaakkola <ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%221%22])">1</ref>.<p>

The Fisher kernel combines the advantages of generative <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../576/27576.xml">
statistical model</link>s (like the <physical_entity wordnetid="100001930" confidence="0.8">
